        <tr><td>Thermostat / cold-control replacement</td><td>$220 – $360</td><td>Mechanical on older, electronic on newer</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor start / run capacitor</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>8–12 year common service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Condenser fan motor replacement</td><td>$260 – $440</td><td>Bottom Freezer and Pro configurations</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Evaporator fan motor replacement</td><td>$240 – $400</td><td>7–10 year common service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Defrost heater / thermostat</td><td>$280 – $480</td><td>Defrost cycle repair</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Bottom Freezer drawer-slide service</td><td>$260 – $440</td><td>6–10 year wear pattern</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Main control board (newer units)</td><td>$400 – $660</td><td>Electronic-control generations</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor replacement (post-warranty)</td><td>$900 – $1,500</td><td>Platform-shared with mainstream brands</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Chrome trim hardware replacement</td><td>Quoted individually</td><td>2–4 week Big Chill factory lead</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Color-matched exterior panel</td><td>Quoted individually</td><td>3–8 week Boulder factory lead</td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Broader refrigerator cost reference: our <a href="/price-list/refrigerator-repair-cost/">refrigerator repair
        cost guide</a>. Retro-specialty sibling: <a href="/brands/smeg-refrigerator-repair/">Smeg refrigerator
        repair</a>. Big Chill hub: <a href="/brands/big-chill/">Big Chill brand hub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Service areas — where our Big Chill calls come from</h2>
      <div class="area-grid">
        <div>
          <h4>Vintage-modern / design-forward (Big Chill heartland)</h4>
          <p>Silver Lake · Echo Park · Los Feliz · Highland Park · Mount Washington · Atwater Village · Venice</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Westside (design-forward kitchens)</h4>
          <p><a href="/beverly-hills/">Beverly Hills</a> · <a href="/santa-monica/">Santa Monica</a> · <a href="/west-hollywood/">West Hollywood</a> · <a href="/brentwood/">Brentwood</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Hollywood Hills + eclectic</h4>
          <p>Hollywood Hills · Laurel Canyon · Nichols Canyon · Mount Olympus · Outpost Estates</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Coastal / beachside cottages</h4>
          <p><a href="/malibu/">Malibu</a> · Venice · Marina del Rey · Manhattan Beach · Palos Verdes</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>San Fernando + San Gabriel Valley</h4>
          <p><a href="/encino/">Encino</a> · Sherman Oaks · Studio City · <a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · South Pasadena · La Cañada</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ventura + Orange County</h4>
          <p><a href="/thousand-oaks/">Thousand Oaks</a> · Westlake Village · Newport Beach · Laguna Beach</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

